                    </label-para>
                  </amend>
                  <follow-text space-before="no">.</follow-text>
                </para>
              </subprov>
              <subprov skeleton="no">
                <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">2</label>
                <para>
                  <text>In section HD 14, in the list of defined terms, <amend.in quote="1">stapled debt security</amend.in> is inserted.</text>
                </para>
